The combination of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_relationship.rep_1"/> and <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_relationship.rep_2"/> shall be unique within a population of <b>shape_definition_3d_intersection</b>.
